  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db6\u0da9\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dcf\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"The current government has hit the teacher in the stomach\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Education Minister and United National Party Vice Leader Mr. Akila Viraj Kariyawasam said that the good governance government took initial steps to solve the teacher's salary issue by taking VAT from profit-making institutions, but as soon as the current government came in, it slashed the VAT and protected big men and hit the teacher in the stomach.",
        "Mr. Kariyawasam said that the government is attacking the public servants and the teachers who voted to bring them to power today. Since the education of the children in this country has been set back by one and a half to two years, both parties should come to a middle ground and solve the problem.",
        "\"A government that has come to power should provide the basic needs of the few people to be fed and clothed. But this government has not been able to pour it. Today, every sector is collapsing,\" said Mr. Kariyawasam."
      ],
